channel.title: [PI] Adding Models (syntax - ::add model <path>?!?!?) [PI]
channel.description: Hey guys im adding custom models (starting with d claws) and ive done everything right, ive made a Raw folder in the chache, ive added the models into it, and im down to where I need to do the "add model" command. When I type it in a box appears asking for the model id, but when i type it in it says model not found. So i tried to be a little more detailed and put 44590.dat (one of the dclaws codes) and it says "syntax - ::add model <path>" what does that mean? Please help me get this command right.
